org.hibernate.jpa.event.spi.jpa

Interface Callback

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractCallback, EntityCallback, ListenerCallback

    public interface Callback
extends java.io.Serializable
    Represents a JPA event callback (the method).

    Generally there are 2 flavors of this; either an annotated method on the entity itself or an annotated method on a separate "listener" class. This contract unifies both of these cases.
